&lt;h2 id=&quot;for-uefi-systems-additional-instructions&quot;&gt;For UEFI systems (additional instructions)&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#for-uefi-systems-additional-instructions&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: for-uefi-systems-additional-instructions&quot; style=&quot;visibility: hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#x27;re on a UEFI system instead of legacy BIOS, here&#x27;s what changes:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;partition-table-for-uefi&quot;&gt;Partition table for UEFI&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#partition-table-for-uefi&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: partition-table-for-uefi&quot; style=&quot;visibility: hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;
